txt.en: 'Are you ready to proceed? Finishing this quest will award completion of Volume III Book 13 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 13 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.

'Are you ready to complete Volume III, Book 13? You will bypass the Battle of the Hornburg.'\n\n'It is your decision. If you would like to skip Volume III Book 13 of the Epic quest, speak to me once more. Meow!'
